{"tid":2394213,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解有「屌你個閪」但冇「屄你條撚」？","createTime":"2021-02-04T04:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T09:38:43.000Z","uid":331972,"like":12,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c9330ba9ee8cfbbdd0cd52bbe9609d0b4eb21fce","tid":2394213,"uid":331972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:32:42.000Z","msg":"問題嚟嘅，點解講粗口冇人講「屄你」（「屄」即「閪」，同音同義）、「屄你條撚」、「屄你老豆」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但明明有時咁講會傳神好多，比如：<br />\n林鄭對連登仔講：「屌你個閪，成Q日叫我做柒婆」 &larr; 呢句冇咩代入感<br />\n<br />\n但如果係：<br />\n林鄭對連登仔講：「<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">再嗌我做柒婆就屄你條撚</span></span>」&larr; 成件事畫面就出哂嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3677514ea5b717c254395a6b9b5ab1d3a284513f","tid":2394213,"uid":176802,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7878ca944166a0270de6f96de0c044e3ca280793","tid":2394213,"uid":153976,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:33:47.000Z","msg":"因為做愛係男性主導"},{"pid":"ce865e3cea492329b059ca411541ed42742d6cee","tid":2394213,"uid":358542,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:36:42.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n根據愛因斯坦相對論，我屌你同你屄我係冇分別"},{"pid":"08b5de8833f1f47133b4f85069037d4561b31f5e","tid":2394213,"uid":23468,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:37:33.000Z","msg":"「含我條撚」"},{"pid":"19692c9a3c37e655234f38dc3086280019390793","tid":2394213,"uid":299514,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:37:51.000Z",